<br>
   As an example,on the Torvo server it is not uncommon to see monks,rogues,and warriors offering to sell ethereal and spectral parchment MQ's - Why in the hell were tanks classes given the oppourtunity to roll on parchments to begin with?Need before greed and when you have a caster in group they need the parchments for thier higher level spells.<br>
<br>
    1st level toons selling 60+ level spells for massive amounts of plat - ok so uber guilds have nothing better to do than try thier best to rape the people in smaller guilds of the money they bust thier asses for and then add insult to injury by putting these items on a toon who cant even cast them.<br>
<br>
    65th level supertwinks who stroll through an area and not ask but TELL you they need KEI as if you are expected to bow down before them because of thier uberness.These are the same people who roll on high level spells such as KEI and Malo even though they may have a character in thier party who needs these spells,just so they can truck on off to the bazaar and try to fetch 10-40k for them.<br>
<br>
   IMO as long as there are people who show off thier bad sides as nothing more than greedy ass money grubbers,then I will ASK for donation before I start to cast and the donation better be more than a measly 1-10pp.Almost all the people who have grown to know me,know I dont look foward to 100pp casts and a typical donation of 40pp is what I have seen.The people who steadily group or talk with me also know kei is thiers for free as are all the people in my guild of course.<br>
<br>
   As for the people who want to charge 10-60k for kei,and up to 100k for VoQ,pony up boys because I have the names written down and you dont get chit for free.Maybe they should start donating level 61+ spells to us chanters for kei or see how they enjoy being S.O.L. on mana regen for raids or groups.<br>
<br>
     Personally I'm of the opinion chanters should strike on all servers until the prices come down on some spells that are more or less group required/expected,and see how many of the uber guilds whine about NEEDING certain spells cast upon members for raids.Strike or sit back and advertise kei casting for 500pp per person,1000pp for group,and heck better make it a nice round 10k for MGB.<br>
<br>
     Want prices to come down on future spells?Dont agree with paying maybe up to 5k for a parchment mq for a spell you might already have?Then its time to give a wake-up call to all the greedy bazaar maggots and Uber-guilds that some things are not free anymore.Just like the spells they are selling. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showMessageRange?topicID=236.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showMessageRange?topicID=236.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showMessageRange?topicID=236.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a> <b>4</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showPrevMessage?topicID=236.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showNextMessage?topicID=236.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=236.topic&index=67><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.threadControl?topicID=236.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/traditional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=236.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub136.ezboard.com/feqenchantersrealmspells.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicI